Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:14.44,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:22.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:46.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:53.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:09.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:13.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:17.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:25.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:34.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:14.44,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}爬上這一帶視野最美的那棵樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:22.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}孩子笑了 笑得天真無邪 她看到了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.63,0:01:46.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}定定地盯著空中暢游的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:53.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}小鎮每個角落裡漸漸褪色的日子浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:57.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}拉鉤上吊百年不變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}即使分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:09.69,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}等待約定實現的心情也寄託在這顆樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:13.80,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一遍一遍地重複
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:17.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每次都止不住淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}停下來又繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:25.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}彷彿是要印證這一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:34.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}山間回音響不絕 你說是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========ED================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:26.26,ED,,0,0,0,,夜の水面に飛び交う蛍が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.12,ED,,0,0,0,,流れ星みたいできれーなのん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.77,ED,,0,0,0,,どこからともない雉鳩の声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.57,ED,,0,0,0,,モノマネしながらいく でこぼこ道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.99,ED,,0,0,0,,澄み渡る星空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.97,ED,,0,0,0,,いつのまにか並んで眠ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,朝日がおかえりって微笑んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:08.50,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一優しい おかえりが待ってる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:13.21,ED,,0,0,0,,さりげない日常 ふわりと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.26,ED,,0,0,0,,抱きしめてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:27.32,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一暖かい 春が訪れる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:38.43,ED,,0,0,0,,ほら 花のこえが聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:26.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}夜晚的水面上飛來飛去的螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}就像是流星一般好美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知何處傳來了雉鳩的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}踏著凹凸不平的小路 邊走邊玩模仿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我們在繁星遍佈的澄空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知不覺就並排著睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}朝陽微笑著歡迎我們回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:08.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最美好的地方 是有人等待我們回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:13.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那些平平淡淡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}輕輕地擁抱我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:27.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最溫暖的地方 是春天到訪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:38.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}豎起耳朵來 能聽到花兒的聲音喔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼就逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要罵我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為肯定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定要什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是又幹什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這池塘裡面沒有生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很寂寥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以去抓點什麼回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很喜歡幹這種事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒那個心情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你零用錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 會給我多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一千円就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我更喜歡諭吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.58,*Default,NTP,270,0,0,,{\fs24}(萬元大鈔)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一千円都不會給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.27,0:00:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是五百円
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我叫大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.67,0:00:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把手錶借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得在門禁時間之前回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:39.51,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H55E66B&\pos(859,590)}大\N家\N一\N起\N去\N賞\N月\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一屆歡樂釣魚大會要在這個池塘開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位玩得開心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木實姐也被叫來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.89,0:02:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是怎麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海突然說要去釣魚賺零用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說我壞話呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起釣魚更有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久沒試過這樣的感覺了 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木實姐喜歡釣魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算很著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前有時也會和小楓和日影一起去釣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 在釣什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要釣碉堡的鯛魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.47,*Default,NTP,80,0,0,,{\fs32}mede-tai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.47,*Default,NTP,280,0,0,,{\fs32}tai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是個池塘 鯛魚是釣不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有鯛魚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想釣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬有時好沒有常識呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不過換成抓貝殼的話 就成了大眼睛的意思了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,360,0,,{\fs32}kai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:41.94,*Default,NTP,400,0,0,,{\fs32}me-dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,380,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H8036E9&\pos(162,104)}me de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,380,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H247CF2&\pos(458,110)}ka i
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,380,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H36AB44&\pos(330,444)}大 眼 睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拼成這種意思有什麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有魚上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎怎怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點拉上來的話就要逃了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉回池塘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉地上的話很可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條很大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚到哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那條也不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了 完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們幾個完全抓不住時機呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 我撿到一大堆貝殼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏也快點釣起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個池塘沒有大魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用麵包可能會比路亞假餌更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假餌是人造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚為什麼會來吃人造的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為形狀很像真的食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有的品種是帶氣味的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚大概會覺得很美味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姐姐咬好聞的橡皮擦是同樣的道理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的班主任都一把年紀了還在幹這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏沒咬呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連小夏也咬橡皮擦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏釣到什麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是這個池塘的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在坐無影凳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是大傢伙 釣到大傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 去叫人來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有水桶可能會不夠大裝不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要去另外準備個容器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H6419DD&\pos(288,366)}mede
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HA23557&\pos(840,366)}想不到（不拼了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H249831&\pos(654,644)}mede
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H6419DD&\pos(308,250)}mede
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H1863F0&\pos(970,250)}求 救(Mayday)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求救信號 這是求救信號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影回來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼岸節回來掃墓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣零食的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好找到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了蓮華 怎麼跑這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚的時候釣到大傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏說釣到池塘的大王了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壽司嗎 姐姐要青花魚壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}註：大王（ぬし）與壽司（すし）讀音略像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大王呀 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是帶去的桶可能放不下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要另外找容器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 貨架上面放著塑膠箱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 我叫到幫手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比想像中的還要大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一直跟它拉鋸很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難對付呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚竿給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有撈網嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只有捕蟲網那樣的 撈不進去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然沒有網
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.49,0:07:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大的魚 沒有網的話 一出水線就會斷呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼說我也沒辦法呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到大王了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到鯉魚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩到各位了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先把這傢伙放到池塘裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 零用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 很大一條魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誇我下誇我下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得有點太大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後你怎麼身上都濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為網太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳進池塘把魚抓上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手錶怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.59,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都忘記戴手錶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然壞了 不過還是再誇我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳進池塘這麼危險 還把手錶弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這邊來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求救 求救 求救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很大一條呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,養起來也很麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想給它起個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『光魚主公』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}註：光魚，用於製作壽司的皮膚有光澤的魚類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好洗乾淨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過都已經中一了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏完全沒有女孩子的樣子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得夏海這樣子和年齡什麼關係都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 想到好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我國中的時候穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木實專門回家拿的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏穿上這個變成女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不需要呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情讓姐姐來不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些衣服確實很可愛 我也想穿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合小鞠尺寸的小學那時的衣服沒有留下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 小夏 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先得把這頭亂糟糟的頭髮梳好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連頭髮都要弄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了 頭髮正是體現女子力的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鞠 有吹風機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更衣室裡面有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帶上衣服一起去換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊還有鏡子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用做到那種程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就按我說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擺出奇怪的姿勢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.25,0:10:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得穿上這身衣服很難活動呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,套了這麼多件沒用的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可愛呀 就像個大小姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 小鞠也這麼覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是很可愛 不過怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:11:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦 莫非姐姐不能跟我一起打扮很不甘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有呢 在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.88,0:11:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把小學時穿過的給你 別生氣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還有完沒完呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被誇可愛的感覺確實很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扮一下大概真的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幹勁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一被人誇就來勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人就會得意忘形 不想誇了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服也換過了 這樣可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都做到這個程度了 再學一下女孩子的言行舉止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,言行舉止我不懂呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要盤腿坐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要正座 正座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 那樣腿會麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐平時是怎麼坐的來著 相撲蹲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一般都是鴨子座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個姿勢我也不習慣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 Stop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要抓頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你說話的口吻也很像男孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連說話方式都要改呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我果然還是沒辦法像個女孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個不認識的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是小夏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給她打扮了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扮 小夏打扮了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件衣服很合身喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 小夏變可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真叫人害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 要給小夏照張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎麼說照片就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照成照片留下來確實更有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我拍了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想拍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了夏海 要拍了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢 很可愛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 快點呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.08,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要擺個可愛的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 用力拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種形象拍了也沒意義呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果誇得太厲害也不行呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 我拿點心來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔喔 謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然回來了我吃了一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃完墓就沒事做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京的生活怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想聽聽東京的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 並不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是糰子呀 怎麼會有糰子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是放在冰箱裡面的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是豆餡的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和綠茶是絕配呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說呀 之前我去橫濱啦 橫濱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橫濱是什麼樣子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有海 有高樓大廈 還有很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京果然很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼大一盒還是一次吃完了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要玩點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在呢在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華也來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 大家都來這了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實今天吃完晚餐大家準備去賞月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到這個季節了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是來提醒一下 不要吃太多零食把肚子撐飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下有糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個絕對不要偷吃冰箱裡面的糰子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我想吃糰子 糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 不會吃不會吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會忍住不吃零食把肚子放空的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那待會見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}糰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}知道了 蓮華…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而已經吃光了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而糰子已經被我們吃光了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就著熱茶一起吃光了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很糟糕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很期待的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬還吵著要吃的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂夏海你做了什麼好事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是賞月糰子的話早說呀 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說別人是笨蛋的才是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不知道 怎麼說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你這個茄子白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看茄子呀 秋天的茄子很美味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是我們兩個內鬥的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然想到了點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好主意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實沒有確認過是不是賞月糰子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一點我道歉 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我連是不是糰子都沒有確認過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 剛才我完全沒看過包裝上面的商品名就打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 剛才的東西很有可能是和糰子味道超像的芋頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真聽你的話真是浪費人生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個世界會有包著豆餡的芋頭呀 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說別人是白痴的才是白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光在這急也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去搗米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能用米做糰子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防萬一夏海失敗了 糰子吃掉的事情露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去把大家的興致降下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呀 影姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這種芋頭都能說出口的人就不要說我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起從興致爆表一下掉到底
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓興致慢慢降下來的話就沒那麼容易向我們發火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掃興的消息慢慢放 我們就能怒火逃生了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原 原來如此 是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有興致呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日影姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐今晚在這住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家決定今晚要在這住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邊吃糰子邊玩到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是這樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 今晚天氣沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會多雲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太期待會比較…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天氣預報說今天是個絕佳的賞月日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過呀 大家也太興奮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是賞月而已喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那麼有趣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次邊吃糰子邊賞月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 其實糰子也可能沒想像中那麼好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來那邊的花瓶什麼都沒插嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來想出去採點芒草回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼賞月的時候要插芒草呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是為了慶祝豐收所以要插稻穗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是採不到稻穗的話就用芒草來代替而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來本來不是用芒草的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家是插稻穗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拜託穗姐就能拿到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那現在就去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都住下的話 我回去把睡衣拿過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的借給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木實好喜歡借衣服給人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而助長了她們的興致了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 你那邊怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成一團漿糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.45,0:18:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說『也』 就是說影姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.28,0:18:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 要道歉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺已經沒辦法了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們裡面最惹不得的是木實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重點向木實下跪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒說過要下跪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向木實下跪的話 應該會原諒我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在木實在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都去我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很快就會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們去玄關跪著等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那樣的話要在蓮醬面前下跪 你沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用同情我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是對著妹妹 不得不道歉的時候也得下跪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開門的時候就一起道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒做好下跪的心理準備呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}吃完晚餐之後我們會邊吃糰子邊賞月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}邊吃糰子邊賞月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}以前的人真懂享受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有糰子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下跪沒用的對手來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呀你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其 其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烏龜 我們在扮烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 影姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回我房間曬太陽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O OK…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 小穗和小楓也來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬叫我們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我家收的米 不介意的話請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 難得有個好時機你說什麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對著賣零食的 下跪沒有用呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我還把媽媽忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是不用在妹妹面前下跪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是被妹妹看見扮烏龜了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 穗姐剛才說帶米過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒收拾好那堆米糊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 影姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼蓮醬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊這邊 很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣零食的和木實姐在用米做五平餅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.54,0:20:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多人的話糰子不夠吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到廚房有搗爛的米 小楓就想到這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.10,0:20:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有前輩拿來的米呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 大救星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼救星？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我和影姐不小心把糰子吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有五平餅的話就沒問題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題… 了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像看起來比平時要大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是中秋明月呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣零食的 我的吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還要點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了吧 五平餅加單
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要五串 快點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
